\" />\n 80 |                 </div>\n 81 |                 <div>\n 82 |                   <h4 className=\"text-[14px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white\">Client Portal Presentation</h4>\n 83 |                   <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF]\">BROWSER / SECURE SOCKET</span>\n 84 |                 </div>\n 85 |               </div>\n 86 |               <p className=\"text-[12.5px] text-white/50 leading-relaxed font-light font-sans\">\n 87 |                 An isolated web console to review task reports, invoices, milestones, and audit trails. Execution logs are loaded on-demand and cached strictly in local transient memory.\n 88 |               </p>\n 89 |             </div>\n 90 | \n 91 |             {/* Block 2: Handshake / Decoupling Tunnel */}\n 92 |             <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4\">\n 93 |               <div className=\"w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-2\">\n 94 |                 <span className=\"h-[1px] flex-grow bg-gradient-to-r from-[#009DFF]/30 to-[#E4000F]/30\" />\n 95 |                 <div className=\"px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg text-[9px] font-mono text-white/60 uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n 96 |                   <Lock className=\"w-3 h-3 text-[#E4000F]\" /> Zero-Trust Handshake\n 97 |                 </div>\n 98 |                 <span className=\"h-[1px] flex-grow bg-gradient-to-r from-[#E4000F]/30 to-[#009DFF]/30\" />\n 99 |               </div>\n100 |               <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/40 text-center max-w-[280px] font-mono leading-relaxed mt-2\">\n101 |                 AES-256 session token pathways keep client secrets invisible to presentation networks.\n102 |               </p>\n103 |             </div>\n104 | \n105 |             {/* Block 3: Live Sovereign Enclaves */}\n106 |             <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-md relativ